Runtime (RDTSC) [s] time

Memory read bandwidth [MBytes/s] 1.0E-06*(MBOX0C0+MBOX0C1+MBOX1C0+MBOX1C1+MBOX2C0+MBOX2C1+MBOX3C0+MBOX3C1+MBOX4C0+MBOX4C1+MBOX5C0+MBOX5C1+MBOX6C0+MBOX6C1+MBOX7C0+MBOX7C1+MBOX8C0+MBOX8C1+MBOX9C0+MBOX9C1+MBOX10C0+MBOX10C1+MBOX11C0+MBOX11C1)*64.0/time
Memory read data volume [GBytes] 1.0E-09*(MBOX0C0+MBOX0C1+MBOX1C0+MBOX1C1+MBOX2C0+MBOX2C1+MBOX3C0+MBOX3C1+MBOX4C0+MBOX4C1+MBOX5C0+MBOX5C1+MBOX6C0+MBOX6C1+MBOX7C0+MBOX7C1+MBOX8C0+MBOX8C1+MBOX9C0+MBOX9C1+MBOX10C0+MBOX10C1+MBOX11C0+MBOX11C1)*64.0
Memory write bandwidth [MBytes/s] 1.0E-06*(MBOX0C2+MBOX0C3+MBOX1C2+MBOX1C3+MBOX2C2+MBOX2C3+MBOX3C2+MBOX3C3+MBOX4C2+MBOX4C3+MBOX5C2+MBOX5C3+MBOX6C2+MBOX6C3+MBOX7C2+MBOX7C3+MBOX8C2+MBOX8C3+MBOX9C2+MBOX9C3+MBOX10C2+MBOX10C3+MBOX11C2+MBOX11C3)*64.0/time
Memory write data volume [GBytes] 1.0E-09*(MBOX0C2+MBOX0C3+MBOX1C2+MBOX1C3+MBOX2C2+MBOX2C3+MBOX3C2+MBOX3C3+MBOX4C2+MBOX4C3+MBOX5C2+MBOX5C3+MBOX6C2+MBOX6C3+MBOX7C2+MBOX7C3+MBOX8C2+MBOX8C3+MBOX9C2+MBOX9C3+MBOX10C2+MBOX10C3+MBOX11C2+MBOX11C3)*64.0
SpecI2M bandwidth [MBytes/s] 1.0E-06*()*64.0/time
SpecI2M data volume [GBytes] 1.0E-09*()*64.0
Memory bandwidth [MBytes/s] 1.0E-06*()*64.0/time
Memory data volume [GBytes] 1.0E-09*()*64.0
SpecI2M ratio 100*()/(MBOX0C2+MBOX0C3+MBOX1C2+MBOX1C3+MBOX2C2+MBOX2C3+MBOX3C2+MBOX3C3+MBOX4C2+MBOX4C3+MBOX5C2+MBOX5C3+MBOX6C2+MBOX6C3+MBOX7C2+MBOX7C3+MBOX8C2+MBOX8C3+MBOX9C2+MBOX9C3+MBOX10C2+MBOX10C3+MBOX11C2+MBOX11C3)

LONG
Formulas:
Memory read bandwidth [MBytes/s] = 1.0E-06*(SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH0_RD)+SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH1_RD))*64.0/runtime
Memory read data volume [GBytes] = 1.0E-09*(SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH0_RD)+SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH1_RD))*64.0
Memory write bandwidth [MBytes/s] = 1.0E-06*(SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH0_WR)+SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH1_WR))*64.0/runtime
Memory write data volume [GBytes] = 1.0E-09*(SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH0_WR)+SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH1_WR))*64.0
SpecI2M bandwidth [MBytes/s] = 1.0E-06*(SUM(TOR_INSERTS_IA_SPECITOM))*64.0/runtime
SpecI2M data volume [GBytes] = 1.0E-09*(SUM(TOR_INSERTS_IA_SPECITOM))*64.0
Memory bandwidth [MBytes/s] = 1.0E-06*(SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH0_RD)+SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH1_RD)+SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH0_WR)+SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH1_WR))*64.0/runtime
Memory data volume [GBytes] = 1.0E-09*(SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH0_RD)+SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH1_RD)+SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH0_WR)+SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH1_WR))*64.0
SpecI2M ratio = 100*SUM(TOR_INSERTS_IA_SPECITOM)/(SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH0_WR)+SUM(CAS_COUNT_SCH1_WR))
--
Profiling group to measure SpecI2M data volume transferred to main memory.
Since this group is based on Uncore events it is only possible to measure on a
per socket base. Some of the counters may not be available on your system.
Also outputs total data volume transferred from/to main memory and memory
bandwidth drawn by all cores of a socket.
